{"lemma":"فاعِلِي","slug":"فاعِلِي","root":"ف.ع.ل","root_slug":"ف-ع-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ع-ل","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فاعِل","root":"فعل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":9},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n34210"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%B9%D9%90%D9%84%D9%90%D9%8A"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"active participle of فَعَلَ (faʕala)","tags":["active","form-i","form-of","participle"],"examples":[{"text":"وَلَا تَقُولَنَّ لِشَيْءٍ إِنِّي فَاعِلٌ ذَلِكَ غَدًا","english":"And do not say with certainty for a thing: surely I will be a doer of that tomorrow."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"effective, efficient"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"doer, one who does something"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"worker"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"subject, agent","tags":["agent","subjective"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb فَعَلَ (faʕala, “to do, to affect”)."},"ipa":["/faːʕil/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34210","headword_ar":"فَاعِلٌ","root":"fEl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[act. part. n. of 1,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Doing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and, used as a subst.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a doer:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a carpenter"},{"kind":"text","text":"is thus"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2421},{"kind":"text","text":"called; accord. to IAar: but it is now peculiarly applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as works with clay,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and builds, and plasters,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and digs foundations:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalapN","text_ar":"فَعَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, K, TA,) as an epithet in which the quality of a subst. predominates, is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"workers in clay"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"digging"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as work with their hands in clay"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"building"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"digging;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalapN","text_ar":"عَمَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmilN","text_ar":"عَامِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakun~aA faAEiliyna","text_ar":"وَكُنَّا فَاعِلِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xxi. 79], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And we were able to do what we willed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@l~a*iyna humo lilz~ak`wpi","text_ar":"وَا@لَّذِينَ هُمْ لِلزَّكٰوةِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEiluwna","text_ar":"فَاعِلُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the same [xxiii. 4], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And who give the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*kwp","text_ar":"ذكوة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poor-rate"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Zj, O, TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who do that which is good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"righteous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Mgh","K","Zj","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}